Noodles & Co. Pasta Fresca
25 min | 5 min prep
SERVES 4

Ingredients
2 tsp extra virgin olive oil
2 1/2 c pre-cooked farfalle (bow-tie) pasta
1/4 c cubed roma tomato
1 Tbsp diced red onion
2 dashes kosher salt, and cracked pepper
1 oz baby fresh spinach

Fresca Sauce
1 Tbsp fresh garlic
1/2 tsp kosher salt
1 Tbsp balsamic vinegar
1 Tbsp sweet white wine
1/4 c extra virgin olive oil

Directions
1) In a very hot saute pan, add: extra virgin olive oil, pre-cooked farfalle
   roma tomatoes, diced red onions, kosher salt & cracked pepper.
2) Sear noodles, stirring occasionally until steaming hot.
3) Add: baby fresh spinach, fresca sauce ingredients
4) Toss to combine, serve with freshly shaved parmesan cheese.
